{"type":"text","timestamp":1782666336438,"sessionID":"ses_0f0cebc45ffeXm04RK0z9p3ABS","part":{"id":"prt_f0f3191df0014DbPR5Uetr7uS6","messageID":"msg_f0f3180d3001mh0NfQ0gbBxUMc","sessionID":"ses_0f0cebc45ffeXm04RK0z9p3ABS","type":"text","text":"The narrow brief points to profile/logout structure and evidence quality rather than a broad app-wide functional omission. I’m checking the exact queue items and current profile implementation to see whether this is a real behavior gap or mainly endpoint/evidence tightening.","time":{"start":1782666334687,"end":1782666336437}}}
